"{\"uid\": \"perthnow.com.au-wa-perth-south-canning-anything-is-possible-23yo-canning-boxer-set-to-represent-australia-in-paris-olympics--c-14368991\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Get the FREE App  Get the FREE App  A family interest saw Yusuf Chothia enrolled in martial arts such as wrestling and kickboxing as a child but it was the release of the 2015 sports drama Creed that ignited a passion for the young athlete to pursue the sport competitively.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 274, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 58, \"end\": 63, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\", \"score\": 0.9999999354979557, \"rank\": 6.380886631105434e-08, \"text\": \"Yusuf\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The first scene where he was punching the wall,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 276, \"to\": 334, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was like, I want to learn how to do that.\", \"from\": 335, \"to\": 379, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I searched up boxing gyms near me and it was Synergy ... and I have been here ever since.\\\"\", \"from\": 381, \"to\": 472, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's now been almost a decade since the 23-year-old first stepped foot in the Canning Vale gym and in a little over three months, he will don green and gold and fight for his country at the 2024 Paris Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 474, \"to\": 689, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The goal was always to have 100 fights, go to the Commonwealth Games and go to the Olympic Games,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 799, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have had about 50 fights, so we are about halfway there.\", \"from\": 801, \"to\": 860, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's one of the dreams, it's a pinch yourself moment, it's super surreal.\\\"\", \"from\": 862, \"to\": 937, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Chothia became the 2023 national champion after a points-based win over Tarique Hipertur at the Australian Elite Championships & Pacific Games qualification event.\", \"from\": 939, \"to\": 1102, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1035, \"end\": 1045, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.999330585366667, \"rank\": 0.0004808752374242041, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is set to represent Australia in the men's 51kg flyweight division in Paris after qualifying late last year.\", \"from\": 1104, \"to\": 1215, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1127, \"end\": 1136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.8539496432062063, \"rank\": 0.16717170466424494, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1177, \"end\": 1182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999722097076, \"rank\": 2.77901999136057e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I had three fights over a week,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 1259, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I broke my hand in the second fight, so I was boxing with one hand pretty much.\", \"from\": 1261, \"to\": 1341, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For the first week, it did not feel like I qualified, it did not feel real.\\\"\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1420, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While Chothia had been lucky with his health, bar cuts or bleeding, he said the broken hand had been his worst injury so far.\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1547, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The hand has been a recurring injury, it got pretty severe at the Pacific Games,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1549, \"to\": 1640, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The first fight went pretty well but I felt the niggle a little bit.\", \"from\": 1642, \"to\": 1711, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It does hurt but you have just got to push through I guess.\\\"\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1774, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the lead-up to Paris, Chothia said his strict training regime would include morning weights sessions, cardio and evening boxing sessions, as well as multiple international and interstate camps.\", \"from\": 1776, \"to\": 1972, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1794, \"end\": 1799, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999722097076, \"rank\": 2.77901999136057e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And while Chothia is a three-time Australian champion, he said the nerves he felt before stepping into the ring never went away.\", \"from\": 1974, \"to\": 2102, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2008, \"end\": 2018, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.999330585366667, \"rank\": 0.0004808752374242041, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They say if you do not get nervous before a fight, you should stop fighting,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2104, \"to\": 2191, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Field Hockey  \\\"If you did not get those butterflies and you did not get those nerves, it would be like going to the shops.\", \"from\": 2193, \"to\": 2315, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's the best worst feeling in the world.\\\"\", \"from\": 2317, \"to\": 2360, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For the young athlete, the journey to Paris is also one self-funded.\", \"from\": 2362, \"to\": 2430, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2400, \"end\": 2405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999722097076, \"rank\": 2.77901999136057e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chothia said while that created financial pressure, a public GoFundMe and the recruitment of sponsors meant things were \\\"working out\\\".\", \"from\": 2432, \"to\": 2566, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am currently not working because it's a full-time gig training for the Olympic Games, it's hard to work when you are travelling so much,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2568, \"to\": 2717, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It has been a bit tough but I have a very supportive family behind me and a great team.\\\"\", \"from\": 2719, \"to\": 2808, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His GoFundMe is still open to donationsonline.\", \"from\": 2810, \"to\": 2856, \"entities\": []}]}"